<p>Open: Vinnie's emotional reaction to discussing Tanya's passing left many viewers in tears, with many also praising the actor for speaking so candidly about his grief</p>

<p>One fan also praised: 'Vinnie Jones was the hard man and tough guy with his football and then in his film career. However it takes alot more than that in his personal life.</p>

